      "description": "First Trust Exchange-Traded Fund VIII - FT Vest U.S. Equity Buffer & Digital Return ETF - July is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by First Trust Advisors LP. It is co-managed by Vest Financial, LLC. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests through derivatives in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It uses derivatives such as FLexible EXchange Options that reference the price performance of the State Street SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust to create its portfolio. The fund invests in growth and value stocks of large-cap companies. First Trust Exchange-Traded Fund VIII - FT Vest U.S. Equity Buffer & Digital Return ETF - July was formed on July 17, 2026 and is domiciled in the United States.",
